    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>BLIXIA is an Adventure-RPG where you can expect casual gameplay in a fantasy world.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Adventure begins here!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the world of BLIXIA and forge your own path. Decide where to journey and how to explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip weapons and armor that match your playstyle, growing stronger and more powerful. Choose diverse spells to help you overcome challenges throughout your adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face enemies ranging from easy to challenging, uncover hidden locations, and collect rare treasures to enhance your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you travel, gather resources to craft even more powerful items. Meet traders who might have rare and useful goods for sale—if you're lucky!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cross paths with characters offering quests to help you on your adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Key Features]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore:</strong> Embark on an epic journey through a beautifully crafted realm, unearth ancient secrets, and brave the depths of mystical caves and other enchanting locales.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294970/extras/45567dcd30a038353142caf3e04fbe25.poster.avif?t=1766430502\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294970/extras/45567dcd30a038353142caf3e04fbe25.webm?t=1766430502\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294970/extras/45567dcd30a038353142caf3e04fbe25.mp4?t=1766430502\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combat:</strong> Choose your fighting style with a variety of weapons. Engage up close, attack from a distance, or cast powerful magic to defeat your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294970/extras/d3cf608607f1fe50fade7851021d800f.poster.avif?t=1766430502\" width=600 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294970/extras/d3cf608607f1fe50fade7851021d800f.webm?t=1766430502\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294970/extras/d3cf608607f1fe50fade7851021d800f.mp4?t=1766430502\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Crafting &amp; Gathering:</strong> Gather essential resources and visit crafting stations to forge powerful items for your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294970/extras/0ae006afee199d758759656f7d2f5fcf.poster.avif?t=1766430502\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294970/extras/0ae006afee199d758759656f7d2f5fcf.webm?t=1766430502\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294970/extras/0ae006afee199d758759656f7d2f5fcf.mp4?t=1766430502\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Quest:</strong> Find quests, complete them, and who knows? You might just stumble upon something extraordinary!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294970/extras/c0b9ac371edb3b4a7f30b4dfcf467872.poster.avif?t=1766430502\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294970/extras/c0b9ac371edb3b4a7f30b4dfcf467872.webm?t=1766430502\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3294970/extras/c0b9ac371edb3b4a7f30b4dfcf467872.mp4?t=1766430502\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Other Features]</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Day &amp; Night Cycle</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shops with Favor Feature</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And more is coming..</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Created by solo developer Micho Schmidt.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Don’t forget to wishlist and follow!</strong></i></p>",
